23
00:01:36,730 --> 00:01:38,620
Open your eyes.

24
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:41,710
Dan Dan, what happened?

25
00:01:41,710 --> 00:01:43,890
Why won't he open his eyes?

26
00:01:43,890 --> 00:01:45,450
Did he hurt his head?

27
00:01:45,450 --> 00:01:50,930
You were with him when he got in the accident. What happened!

28
00:01:50,930 --> 00:01:53,830
