33
00:02:05,810 --> 00:02:08,330
Noona, calm down.

34
00:02:08,330 --> 00:02:11,620
Why are you being harsh to Dan Dan? She must have been shocked.

35
00:02:11,620 --> 00:02:14,580
Honey, what should I do?

36
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:17,410
Honey, don't leave me.

37
00:02:17,410 --> 00:02:19,370
Sister-in-law, calm down.

38
00:02:19,370 --> 00:02:21,700
Why would he die?

39
