Dan Dan, did the doctor examine him?

40
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:26,000
What did they say?

41
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,080
Fortunately, he's fine everywhere else.

42
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:33,990
But he had a slight fracture on his left arm, so they did a soft cast.

43
00:02:33,990 --> 00:02:36,950
Is that really the case?

44
00:02:36,950 --> 00:02:38,380
Nothing else's wrong?

45
00:02:38,380 --> 00:02:42,790
But he had a slight injury to his head.

46
00:02:42,790 --> 00:02:45,590
So he needed to be admitted for further tests.

47
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:48,780
The results will be out in the morning.

48
00:02:48,780 --> 00:02:52,040
Does he need further tests?

49
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:56,090
Could he be in a vegetative state?

50
00:02:56,090 --> 00:02:57,980
Oh, no! What do we do?

51
00:02:57,980 --> 00:03:01,020
Sister-in-law, how can you say such unspeakable things?

52
00:03:01,020 --> 00:03:02,960
How can you say a vegetative human?

53
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,620
She's right, Yeon Sil.

54
00:03:04,620 --> 00:03:07,270
How can you speak so carelessly?

55
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:10,810
