56
00:03:10,810 --> 00:03:12,730
Mom, Father will be fine.

57
00:03:12,730 --> 00:03:16,510
So please calm down.

58
00:03:18,350 --> 00:03:20,250
Mom, uncle has opened his eyes.

59
00:03:20,250 --> 00:03:22,710
Yes, he has.

60
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:26,100
Can you see me, Honey?

61
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:28,480
Soo Chul, Soo Chul, this is your sister.

62
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:32,600
Your sister. Can you see all of your family here?

63
00:03:33,970 --> 00:03:36,920
- Yes.
- Oh, Honey.

64
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:39,010
Oh, Honey.

65
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:42,320
- It's good.
- Dan Dan.

66
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,930
Dad.

67
00:03:43,930 --> 00:03:46,370
Are you alright?

68
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:51,120
Dan Dan. You can never be with Chairman Lee.

69
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,380
Please don't go there.

70
00:03:53,380 --> 00:03:55,620
Please stay at home, okay?

71
00:03:55,620 --> 00:04:01,520
Dad. Why are you acting like this?

72
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,480
Hey, Park Dan Dan!

73
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,820
What's wrong with her?

74
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:13,620
Honey...

75
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:18,910
Chairman, my dad...

76
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:24,210
My dad got into an accident because of me.

77
00:04:24,210 --> 00:04:26,260
What are you saying?

78
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:31,090
Ms. Park. Please tell me what happened calmly.

79
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:34,250
That is...

80
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:38,260
I was running away from home.

81
00:04:38,260 --> 00:04:43,640
My dad was following me on his motorcycle.

82
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:46,980
And he got into an accident.

83
00:04:46,980 --> 00:04:49,850
So, we are in an emergency room.

84
00:04:49,850 --> 00:04:54,200
He just barely woke up.

85
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:57,680
Even in that state,

86
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:02,050
he told me to break up with you.

87
00:05:02,050 --> 00:05:05,730
What do we do, Chairman?

88
00:05:05,730 --> 00:05:08,000
Ms. Park.

89
00:05:08,010 --> 00:05:09,560
Which hospital are you at?

90
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:12,150
I will go there now.

91
00:05:14,570 --> 00:05:16,620
When the test results come out tomorrow morning,

92
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:18,750
he will be discharged unless something shows up.

93
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:20,370
Please go home, Sister-in-law.

94
00:05:20,370 --> 00:05:21,930
I will stay here.

95
00:05:21,930 --> 00:05:26,360
Yes, please, Noona. Please take your mom home, Joon Oh.

96
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,120
- Yes.
- Sister-in-law.

97
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:31,950
Please call me as soon as you get the result. Okay?

98
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,690
Yes, Sister-in-law.

99
00:05:33,690 --> 00:05:35,520
You should take mom home too, Geon.

100
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:38,840
And Dae Beom, please finish the closing at the store.

101
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:42,060
Okay. Let's go, Grandma and Uncle.

102
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:44,360
Dan Dan, go home with your grandma as well.

103
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,900
No, Mom. I will go later.

104
00:05:46,900 --> 00:05:49,310
Sure. Dan Dan should stay.

105
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:52,900
She won't feel right staying at home.

106
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:56,640
We will go now. Stay with your mom.

107
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,370
- Yes.
- Let's go.

108
00:05:58,370 --> 00:06:00,690
Please rest, Brother-in-law. We'll get going now.

109
00:06:00,690 --> 00:06:02,910
Go ahead.

110
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:10,990
Please go and get us something to drink.

111
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:14,350
I have something to discuss with Dan Dan.

112
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:17,760
What?

113
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:20,120
Okay.

114
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:33,540
Can he not speak in my presence?

115
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:36,880
He's constantly excluding me and talking to each other.

116
00:06:36,910 --> 00:06:40,050
If he weren't injured, I would have hit him once.

117
00:06:40,050 --> 00:06:44,280
This is why Dan Dan doesn't take me seriously.

118
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:51,420
Dan Dan.

119
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:55,900
Because you work in that house and see Chairman Lee every day,

120
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:58,180
it won't be easy to end your feelings for him.

121
00:06:58,180 --> 00:07:02,200
So like I told you, you should quit right now and leave that house.

122
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:04,100
If you don't see him,

123
00:07:04,100 --> 00:07:08,730
you will forget about him in no time, like magic.

124
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,160
Dad.

125
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:16,420
My feeling for the Chairman is not a momentary emotion.

126
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:20,570
I thought about it over and over if this was the right thing to do.

127
00:07:20,570 --> 00:07:23,160
No matter how much I think about it,

128
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:26,860
my feelings for the Chairman are genuine.

129
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:30,370
I... like him a lot.

130
00:07:30,370 --> 00:07:32,350
So Dad,

131
00:07:32,350 --> 00:07:36,400
can't you just trust me and watch?

132
00:07:36,410 --> 00:07:40,050
- Dad, please.
- Park Dan Dan.

133
00:07:40,050 --> 00:07:41,630
When I'm begging you like this,

134
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:43,800
won't you listen to me?

135
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:47,750
This is something that shouldn't happen. It shouldn't!

136
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,930
I came after hearing you got injured.

137
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:59,710
- How are you feeling?
- How dare you come here?

138
00:07:59,710 --> 00:08:01,910
With whose permission?

139
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:03,800
Leave immediately. Right now!

140
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,180
Why are you doing this, Dad?

141
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:07,630
I told him that you were hurt,

142
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:10,690
so he came because he was worried about you.

143
00:08:10,690 --> 00:08:13,770
It feels like this happened because of me. I'm so sorry.

144
00:08:13,770 --> 00:08:16,660
I don't want to hear that from you!

145
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:19,200
Dan Dan will quit working at that house.

146
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:21,550
So please pack all her things and send them to us!

147
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:23,380
Dad.

148
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:26,950
For someone at your age, what are you doing with a young child?

149
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:29,390
Are you not embarrassed?

150
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:31,200
Dad, you're going too far!

151
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:32,970
Honey, calm down.

152
00:08:32,970 --> 00:08:34,600
Tell this person to leave.

153
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:38,960
Chairman, I think it would be best if you left for today.

154
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:42,710
Because of his accident, he's not in good shape.

155
00:08:42,710 --> 00:08:45,380
Why don't you talk with him next time?

156
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:47,240
Okay.

157
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:49,800
I'm sorry.

158
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:52,200
Please get well soon.

159
00:08:52,210 --> 00:08:55,150
Dad, I'm telling you clearly.

160
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,930
Even if you act like this,

161
00:08:56,930 --> 00:08:59,350
I won't ever break up with the Chairman.

162
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:01,220
I'm really sorry,

163
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:03,540
but I'm going to leave with the Chairman.

164
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:05,160
Let's go.

165
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:07,560
Dan Dan, you stay there!

166
00:09:08,900 --> 00:09:11,290
Let's leave now.

167
00:09:11,290 --> 00:09:14,730
Ms. Park, just stay here.

168
00:09:14,730 --> 00:09:17,950
Stay with your father and take care of him today.

169
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:20,220
Please do so.

170
00:09:21,970 --> 00:09:23,940
Then, I'll be leaving.

171
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:26,180
Goodbye.

172
00:09:36,260 --> 00:09:39,310
Dad, you're going overboard.

173
00:09:39,310 --> 00:09:41,880
Chairman came all the way here to see you.

174
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:43,850
I will see him off, at least.

175
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:46,720
- Dan Dan. Park Dan Dan!
- Honey.

176
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:50,590
She will only see him off. Let her go.

177
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:19,060
Oh, my goodness!

178
00:10:20,650 --> 00:10:23,260
It's just me.

179
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:26,360
Why are you so startled?

180
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:30,210
I was surprised since you suddenly hugged me from behind.

181
00:10:30,210 --> 00:10:33,980
Why would you be surprised like that?

182
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:42,430
Aren't I the only woman in the world who can hug you from behind?

183
00:10:42,430 --> 00:10:46,530
That is true. But it was so unexpected.

184
00:10:46,530 --> 00:10:49,820
Why are you out here when I told you to stay there?

185
00:10:49,820 --> 00:10:55,040
Since you came all the way here, I wanted to walk you to the parking lot.

186
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:57,410
Let's go.

187
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:04,660
Don't you like it that I've come to see you off like this?

188
00:11:04,660 --> 00:11:07,630
Are you touched?

189
00:11:07,630 --> 00:11:11,100
I like it. I'm touched.

190
00:11:15,330 --> 00:11:18,140
We got here so quickly.

191
00:11:20,300 --> 00:11:22,520
I can't help it.

192
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:25,180
I will walk you back inside.

193
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:26,740
It's okay.

194
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:31,530
I've come to see you off, so please go on home.

195
00:11:31,530 --> 00:11:37,500
Then, I will go after I see you go inside. Please go inside first.

196
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:39,450
Please go first, Chairman.

197
00:11:39,450 --> 00:11:44,680
I will go after I see you off.

198
00:11:45,930 --> 00:11:49,440
I can't stop your stubbornness.

199
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,930
I give in.

200
00:12:01,050 --> 00:12:04,080
It's cold out. Please go inside.

201
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:07,820
Chairman. Fighting!

202
00:12:07,820 --> 00:12:11,210
Yes. Fighting!

203
00:12:11,210 --> 00:12:14,300
- I'm going.
- Yes.

204
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:29,590
I'm sorry, Chairman.

205
00:12:29,590 --> 00:12:33,030
What should we do, really?

206
00:12:48,460 --> 00:12:51,200
What's going to happen with Dan Dan?

207
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:54,740
I don't think my uncle will approve till the end.

208
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:58,880
I also think he won't approve.

209
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:04,380
But I never thought that Dan Dan would have such a shocking relationship.

210
00:13:04,380 --> 00:13:10,130
I only saw this kind of relationship in TV shows or movies, not in real life.

211
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:16,050
Even among my friends, I don't know anyone dating an older man.

212
00:13:16,050 --> 00:13:22,760
I think uncle is more bothered by him being the father of three children than his age.

213
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:26,640
I don't know any couple like that either.

214
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:29,820
They are a shocking couple.

215
00:13:29,820 --> 00:13:32,160
What would you do in their shoes?

216
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:36,240
What if your daughter was in such a relationship in the future?

217
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:42,940
Hey, you are going too far. I'm not even married, and how can I be thinking of a daughter?

218
00:13:42,940 --> 00:13:45,920
I said, what if!

219
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:53,770
Actually, we are more of a problem than Dan Dan.

220
00:13:53,770 --> 00:13:57,360
Joon Oh, what's going to happen to us?

221
00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:00,280
We are not a shocking couple at all.

222
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:04,890
Just that we are in-laws, that's the only thing.

223
00:14:04,890 --> 00:14:09,900
So Mi Rim, do not worry.

224
00:14:09,930 --> 00:14:14,750
Mi Rim, why don't we go over there and have a fish cake?

225
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,930
Okay.

226
00:14:23,490 --> 00:14:26,360
Daughter-in-law, I need some money.

227
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:30,050
Not too much, just a little. About 50 million won.

228
00:14:30,050 --> 00:14:35,900
My friends and I are going to Hawaii for a vacation.

229
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:43,240
Mother-in-law, I've told you many times already.

230
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:47,230
I can't give you any more than your allowance.

231
00:14:47,230 --> 00:14:50,050
So you will need to go on a trip within your allowance budget.

232
00:14:50,050 --> 00:14:54,640
I'm saying I'm not just crossing the Han River.

233
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:58,780
We are going to Hawaii. Hawaii.

234
00:14:58,780 --> 00:15:05,790
But still, my husband told me not to give you any other money than your allowance.

235
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:10,170
Absolutely not! You know that he said that.

236
00:15:10,170 --> 00:15:14,330
So I will pretend I didn't hear your request. Okay?

237
00:15:14,330 --> 00:15:18,050
Honey, my darling, I'm home!

238
00:15:18,050 --> 00:15:21,670
Oh, my husband is here!

239
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:35,680
Honey, my darling. I bought a diamond necklace for you.

240
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:40,390
Oh, Baby! Thank you so much.

241
00:15:40,390 --> 00:15:43,840
These diamonds are so big!

242
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:46,700
They are beautiful.

243
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:50,660
- Do you like it, Baby?
- Yes, I love it.

244
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:55,930
It's more beautiful because the rock is big. I love it very, very much!

245
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:17,850
It freaks me out just thinking about it.

246
00:16:17,850 --> 00:16:21,610
What should I do if that ever really happens?

247
00:16:21,610 --> 00:16:25,450
No, no. That can't happen.

248
00:16:25,450 --> 00:16:28,030
Yes, I have to split them up.

249
00:16:28,030 --> 00:16:32,380
I have to destroy the entire fraudulent family.

250
00:16:32,380 --> 00:16:35,690
It's no time for me to be idle.

251
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:44,760
Oh, what brings you to my house?

252
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:48,740
Right! Are you here to apologize to me?

253
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:51,580
Hey, the head of the fraudsters.

254
00:16:51,580 --> 00:16:55,150
No matter how much you love money.

255
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:57,730
How could you covet our Chairman Lee?

256
00:16:57,730 --> 00:17:00,090
You couldn't make it work with my Se Ryun.

257
00:17:00,090 --> 00:17:04,590
So you turned your niece into a gold digger to take over the Madam of the house?

258
00:17:04,590 --> 00:17:05,980
What?

259
00:17:05,980 --> 00:17:09,620
What did you say? A gold digger?

260
00:17:09,620 --> 00:17:13,610
Are you talking about our Dan Dan now?

261
00:17:13,610 --> 00:17:17,820
Yes, you, head of the fraudsters. You planned this all out, didn't you?

262
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:24,640
How can such a young girl go after our Chairman Lee? Isn't that a gold digger?

263
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:27,630
Get her off of our Young Gook this minute.

264
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:29,950
Take your niece out of our house!

265
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:32,290
If you don't, I will not be quiet.

