577
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:41,630
With who's permission?

578
00:37:41,630 --> 00:37:43,610
Even if the world collapses, that won't happen.

579
00:37:43,610 --> 00:37:47,640
So leave Korea right now.

580
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:50,930
You better think wisely.

