597
00:38:56,750 --> 00:38:59,700
What should I do?

598
00:39:17,750 --> 00:39:19,940
Father.

599
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:33,350
Father. Why are you doing this?

600
00:39:33,350 --> 00:39:35,380
Chairman.

601
00:39:35,380 --> 00:39:39,690
Please, I'm begging you.

602
00:39:39,690 --> 00:39:45,170
Please break up with my Dan Dan.

603
00:39:45,170 --> 00:39:50,980
Please let her go.

604
00:39:50,980 --> 00:39:53,490
I'm begging you like this.

605
00:39:53,490 --> 00:39:57,330
You have a daughter too.

606
00:39:57,330 --> 00:40:02,300
Please think about this once from the perspective of a daughter's father.

607
00:40:02,300 --> 00:40:05,680
Dan Dan is only 27.

608
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:09,900
She's a young lady with a future ahead of her.

609
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:12,730
Chairman.

610
00:40:12,730 --> 00:40:17,280
What should I do for you to break up with her?

611
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:20,780
I will do anything you ask.

612
00:40:20,780 --> 00:40:22,690
So please,

613
00:40:22,690 --> 00:40:24,970
let her go.

614
00:40:24,970 --> 00:40:27,720
Please, I'm begging you.

615
00:40:33,490 --> 00:40:36,230
As a fellow father,

616
00:40:36,230 --> 00:40:40,670
please think about Dan Dan just once.

617
00:40:46,010 --> 00:40:50,960
I understand what you are saying.

618
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:53,220
So, please...

619
00:40:53,220 --> 00:40:55,870
Please stand up.

620
00:41:05,540 --> 00:41:07,520
Thank you.

621
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:10,670
Chairman.

622
00:41:10,670 --> 00:41:14,330
I...

623
00:41:14,330 --> 00:41:17,660
I'll trust you.

624
00:41:57,440 --> 00:42:00,520
Ms. Park.

625
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:03,300
Chairman.

626
00:42:27,260 --> 00:42:29,510
Chairman.

627
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:34,210
For me...

628
00:42:34,210 --> 00:42:37,610
When I turned 20,

629
00:42:37,610 --> 00:42:40,880
I felt like I had become an adult.

630
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:43,570
And I started working,

631
00:42:43,570 --> 00:42:45,650
received a salary,

632
00:42:45,650 --> 00:42:50,450
and got the confidence that I could live on my own.

633
00:42:50,450 --> 00:42:53,940
So I thought, now I'm an adult,

634
00:42:53,940 --> 00:43:01,450
and I can live my life the way I want, doing what I want.

635
00:43:01,450 --> 00:43:06,980
But, the life that I've lived until now

636
00:43:06,980 --> 00:43:10,440
wasn't only with my own strength.

637
00:43:13,190 --> 00:43:20,350
My parents and my family's sacrifice made it possible.

638
00:43:20,350 --> 00:43:23,690
I had forgotten about that.

639
00:43:23,690 --> 00:43:31,300
I love my dad more than anyone in this world.

640
00:43:31,300 --> 00:43:36,570
Just like you loved your mother.

641
00:43:38,330 --> 00:43:45,120
My loving dad is even kneeling to oppose our relationship.

642
00:43:45,120 --> 00:43:49,500
I was hurting him that much...

643
00:43:51,870 --> 00:43:59,350
I told you many times not to change our minds.

644
00:43:59,350 --> 00:44:05,910
I'm so sorry to make this conclusion.

645
00:44:05,910 --> 00:44:08,700
Ms. Park.

646
00:44:08,700 --> 00:44:11,930
I understand what you are saying.

647
00:44:11,930 --> 00:44:17,210
So, you don't have to say anything more if it's too hard.

648
00:44:19,620 --> 00:44:21,610
I'll tell the kids

649
00:44:21,610 --> 00:44:23,420
that I'm quitting.

650
00:44:23,420 --> 00:44:26,710
Then, excuse me first.

651
00:44:51,360 --> 00:44:53,710
Dad.

652
00:44:53,710 --> 00:44:57,050
I broke up with the Chairman.

653
00:44:59,040 --> 00:45:00,900
Really?

654
00:45:00,900 --> 00:45:03,100
Yes.

655
00:45:08,870 --> 00:45:14,090
Thank you, Dan Dan.

656
00:45:14,100 --> 00:45:18,240
But Dad, just because I broke up with him,

657
00:45:18,240 --> 00:45:21,440
I can't quit my work immediately.

658
00:45:21,440 --> 00:45:25,330
I have to work until they get another tutor for the children.

659
00:45:25,330 --> 00:45:27,340
You understand that, right?

660
00:45:27,340 --> 00:45:30,740
Well, as long as you're certain,

661
00:45:30,740 --> 00:45:32,730
that's fine.

662
00:45:34,260 --> 00:45:36,150
Then I'll be going.

663
00:45:36,150 --> 00:45:38,250
Dan Dan.

664
00:45:38,250 --> 00:45:41,990
You can't change your mind. You promise me.

665
00:45:41,990 --> 00:45:46,080
- You're really ending it with Chairman Lee.
- Yes.

666
00:45:46,080 --> 00:45:48,210
Don't worry.

667
00:45:48,210 --> 00:45:51,840
Dad, I'm leaving now.

668
00:46:10,880 --> 00:46:15,820
Chairman, this is Dan Dan's father.

669
00:46:15,820 --> 00:46:18,590
Yes, please speak.

