672
00:46:29,500 --> 00:46:31,410
Yes.

673
00:46:31,410 --> 00:46:33,820
We broke up.

674
00:46:37,510 --> 00:46:40,020
Thank you.

675
00:46:40,020 --> 00:46:42,580
But, Chairman.

676
00:46:42,580 --> 00:46:45,950
I'm sorry, but I have one more thing to ask you.

677
00:46:45,950 --> 00:46:49,670
Please find a new tutor for the children quickly.

678
00:46:49,670 --> 00:46:52,560
So that Dan Dan can leave that house.

679
00:46:52,560 --> 00:46:57,260
Being in the same house would be uncomfortable for both of you.

680
00:46:58,660 --> 00:47:01,570
Yes. I'll do that.

681
00:47:01,570 --> 00:47:04,160
Don't worry.

682
00:47:04,160 --> 00:47:07,070
I'll leave it to you then.

683
00:47:35,770 --> 00:47:38,830
Ajussi.

684
00:47:38,830 --> 00:47:41,020
How did you know that I was here?

