689
00:47:53,020 --> 00:47:57,020
We decided to be friends. Does it make sense for a friend not to know this?

690
00:47:57,020 --> 00:47:59,130
When did I say I would be your friend?

691
00:47:59,130 --> 00:48:01,220
Let's just be friends.

692
00:48:01,220 --> 00:48:03,390
I became your friend when we first met.

693
00:48:03,390 --> 00:48:05,870
You should leave now. I'm busy.

694
00:48:05,870 --> 00:48:09,360
The flower shop is pretty.

695
00:48:09,360 --> 00:48:11,470
It suits you.

696
00:48:11,470 --> 00:48:13,380
Ajussi.

697
00:48:13,380 --> 00:48:16,070
I came to buy flowers.

698
00:48:16,070 --> 00:48:20,220
Please make me a pretty carnation flower bouquet.

699
00:48:20,220 --> 00:48:22,550
Carnations?

