00:48:22,550 --> 00:48:24,870
It's for my mom.

701
00:48:50,010 --> 00:48:52,920
What kind of flower is this?

702
00:48:54,380 --> 00:48:56,720
It's Ranunculus.

703
00:48:58,150 --> 00:49:00,780
And this one?

704
00:49:00,780 --> 00:49:02,200
It's Delphinium.

705
00:49:02,200 --> 00:49:05,550
Del... Delphi... It's so difficult.

706
00:49:05,550 --> 00:49:08,420
And this?

707
00:49:08,420 --> 00:49:10,170
It's roses.

708
00:49:10,170 --> 00:49:12,030
Do you not know roses?

709
00:49:12,030 --> 00:49:14,630
It's a Victoria Rose.

710
00:49:14,630 --> 00:49:16,800
Oh, it's a rose.

711
00:49:16,800 --> 00:49:19,310
I know what a rose is.

712
00:49:20,530 --> 00:49:23,060
Please wrap up the rest.

713
00:49:36,800 --> 00:49:41,500
Young Gook, seeing what happened to you.

714
00:49:41,500 --> 00:49:45,340
I feel like it's all my fault.

715
00:49:45,340 --> 00:49:51,950
After what happened to Young Ae, I felt like you had found the right person.

716
00:49:51,950 --> 00:49:54,760
So I was very happy.

717
00:49:54,760 --> 00:50:00,560
That's why I encouraged you to go for it.

718
00:50:00,560 --> 00:50:03,710
All the stuff you were worried about,

719
00:50:03,710 --> 00:50:10,130
I might not have taken them seriously.

720
00:50:12,520 --> 00:50:15,150
I'm sorry, Young Gook.

