00:50:18,580 --> 00:50:23,920
As a person raising children,

722
00:50:23,920 --> 00:50:29,030
I can understand where Ms. Park's father is coming from.

723
00:50:29,030 --> 00:50:33,860
That's why you chose to end the relationship, I'm sure.

