00:53:23,210 --> 00:53:27,500
Just wrap things up and forget about everything.

753
00:53:27,500 --> 00:53:30,190
Ms. Park.

754
00:53:30,190 --> 00:53:32,820
Don't worry about me.

755
00:53:32,820 --> 00:53:34,960
I'm fine.

756
00:53:34,960 --> 00:53:39,370
I am really okay.

757
00:53:39,370 --> 00:53:44,560
But I worry that you might have a hard time.

758
00:53:44,560 --> 00:53:50,080
♫ Why do you run away love, like a shy child? ♫

