00:54:10,710 --> 00:54:18,810
♫ I have to abandon the longing and the grief ♫

764
00:54:18,810 --> 00:54:24,900
♫ What am I looking for on this road wandering? ♫

765
00:54:24,900 --> 00:54:32,550
♫ Why am I here for what? ♫

766
00:54:36,760 --> 00:54:40,810
Dan Dan, what are you saying right now?

767
00:54:40,810 --> 00:54:45,250
As you said, I was really going to break up with the Chairman.

768
00:54:45,250 --> 00:54:51,020
