769
00:54:51,020 --> 00:54:55,330
I know you want me to be happy.

770
00:54:55,330 --> 00:54:58,490
You are worried that it will be difficult for me to be with the Chairman.

771
00:54:58,490 --> 00:55:01,660
But Dad, I can be happy with him.

772
00:55:01,660 --> 00:55:04,350
I don't think I can break up with him.

773
00:55:04,350 --> 00:55:07,460
Can't you give in just this once?

774
00:55:07,460 --> 00:55:12,880
Dan Dan. It's not easy breaking up with someone you once liked.

775
00:55:12,880 --> 00:55:16,760
But if you endure a little, time will heal everything.

776
00:55:16,760 --> 00:55:22,750
Dad. I don't think I could ever forget Chairman.

777
00:55:22,750 --> 00:55:25,770
I think I really love him.

778
00:55:25,770 --> 00:55:30,050
Dan Dan, but you promised me to break up with him.

779
00:55:30,050 --> 00:55:33,270
Why are you making me upset?

780
00:55:33,270 --> 00:55:36,040
Get out of that house now.

781
00:55:36,040 --> 00:55:39,450
Don't wait until they find a new tutor.

782
00:55:40,890 --> 00:55:42,410
Okay.

783
00:55:42,410 --> 00:55:45,000
Fine. I'm sorry.

784
00:55:45,000 --> 00:55:47,130
Dan Dan.

785
00:55:47,130 --> 00:55:49,180
- Dan Dan!
- Honey.

786
00:55:49,180 --> 00:55:52,810
Can't you just let her be with him?

